List of KEGG pathways

Source: R/kegg.R
kegg_pathway_list.Rd

Retrieves a list of available KEGG pathways.

kegg_pathway_list()

Value

Data frame of pathway names and identifiers.

See also

  • kegg_process

  • kegg_pathway_download

  • kegg_pathways_download

  • kegg_open

  • kegg_picture

  • kegg_info

Examples

kegg_pws <- kegg_pathway_list()
